00:00:35,620 --> 00:00:39,260
Mast! Lay down the mast!

2
00:00:44,660 --> 00:00:46,900
Hurry up and get the rope!

3
00:00:48,220 --> 00:00:50,900
Bow and stern face the banks! Quick!

4
00:00:54,580 --> 00:00:56,980
Thousands of homes are brightly lit,

5
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:59,420
and the doors to them are wide open.

6
00:00:59,420 --> 00:01:01,580
This is East Capital.

7
00:01:02,180 --> 00:01:05,180
New wine from Sunyang Restaurant!

8
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:07,700
Welcome to enjoy it!

9
00:01:07,860 --> 00:01:10,380
If you want to know what happens next,

10
00:01:10,380 --> 00:01:12,460
wait until next time.

11
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:14,980
People from all over the world gather here,

12
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:17,940
and envoys from various countries come to communicate with the authorities.

13
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:24,660
[Riverside Code at Qingming Festival]

14
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,660
[Adapted from Ye Wenbiao's Novel Series of the Same Name]

15
00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:27,980
[Episode 21]

16
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:28,780
["Heavenly principles shine like a beacon,]

17
00:01:28,780 --> 00:01:29,980
[leaving nothing concealed." by Zhang Zai, Northern Song]

18
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,190
The serious matters are finished,

19
00:01:32,910 --> 00:01:35,080
so can we

20
00:01:35,630 --> 00:01:36,440
enjoy ourselves a little now?

21
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:37,510
Alright.

22
00:01:37,510 --> 00:01:38,720
Then,

23
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:41,160
who will act as the brush today?

24
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,510
Everyone is entertaining the guests.

25
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,380
Then find

26
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:57,550
the most useless one.

27
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:00,120
No, don't!

28
00:02:00,550 --> 00:02:01,480
No, don't!

29
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:04,870
These paintings,

30
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:07,080
created near the Women's Aid Society,

31
00:02:07,630 --> 00:02:08,630
are all recent works.

32
00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:11,470
Mr. Zhao,

33
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:12,270
this one

34
00:02:12,270 --> 00:02:13,670
was painted this morning.

35
00:02:15,110 --> 00:02:16,800
Why is this carriage parked here?

36
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,750
This carriage

37
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:19,030
seems to be delivering goods

38
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:20,320
for the Women's Aid Society.

39
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,470
What about

40
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:23,000
this big barrel on the carriage?

41
00:02:23,270 --> 00:02:24,110
It's a wine barrel.

42
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,080
I wondered the same while painting:

43
00:02:26,110 --> 00:02:27,600
Why would the Women's Aid Society

44
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,190
need so much wine?

45
00:02:29,830 --> 00:02:30,520
Exactly.

46
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:31,880
It's a wine barrel,

47
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:33,470
but it might not actually contain wine.

48
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,320
What about the mark on the horse?

49
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:38,600
It's a branding mark.

50
00:02:38,670 --> 00:02:39,720
It's a fish symbol.

51
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,670
This horse belongs to Yayuan Mansion.

52
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:57,190
Drop her down!

53
00:03:05,270 --> 00:03:07,800
Drunken strokes, heaven's grace unfolds,

54
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:10,830
A rainbow's arc in beauty told.

55
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,630
Thank you, brush, for accompanying me,

56
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:18,450
In this quiet, peaceful sphere.

57
00:03:19,550 --> 00:03:21,960
Mr. Luan, your literary talent

58
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,180
rivals that of Su Shi!

59
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,630
Hurry, give it a try!

60
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,670
Alright, no rush.

61
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,630
Let her go.

62
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,000
Drop her down.

63
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,030
Let her go!

64
00:03:32,550 --> 00:03:34,240
Let me go!

65
00:03:34,290 --> 00:03:36,030
Please, I beg you!

66
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:38,390
You ruthless bastards!

67
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,960
Pull her up!

68
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,390
Let her go!

69
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,270
Stop writing!

70
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,160
Stop writing!

71
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,750
It's ink.

72
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:06,190
This person's hair, nose, and mouth

73
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:07,160
are all stained with ink.

74
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,960
The head was dipped in ink,

75
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,000
and there are slight bruises behind the ears.

76
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:14,360
This person was likely hung upside down for a long time before death.

77
00:04:21,540 --> 00:04:24,920
[Elegance]

78
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,000
How is it?

79
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,440
Good.

80
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:29,600
[Elegance]
The ink breathes brilliance,

81
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,830
strokes dance with dynamic flair,

82
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:32,640
a masterpiece beyond compare!

83
00:04:34,070 --> 00:04:35,760
Like dragons and serpents in motion,

84
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:37,440
peaks rise in countless forms.

85
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,440
Even

86
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,200
the wild strokes of masters Zhang and Huai

87
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,670
or the rebirth of the grass-script masters,

88
00:04:42,670 --> 00:04:44,480
could hardly surpass this artistry!

89
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:47,350
Wonderful! Such elegance

90
00:04:47,350 --> 00:04:48,920
is truly extraordinary!

91
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,270
I have learned so much.

92
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:51,230
This

93
00:04:51,230 --> 00:04:54,950
is indeed my masterpiece.

94
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,550
Mrs. Xie!

95
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,830
It's ruined!

96
00:05:01,790 --> 00:05:03,670
You wretched scum!

97
00:05:03,670 --> 00:05:05,720
You ruined my masterpiece!

98
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,110
How dare you destroy my work!

99
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:11,880
Stop hitting her!

100
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:12,720
You ruined my masterpiece!

101
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,350
Stop it!

102
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:17,350
Instead of saving people, you're fighting!

103
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,160
Stop it!

104
00:05:20,230 --> 00:05:21,200
Stop it!

105
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:24,830
You beast, stop this madness!

106
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:33,440
Scream!

107
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,720
Go on, scream again!

108
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:41,510
Don't worry.

109
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:45,320
We have plenty of tricks.

110
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:48,040
You'll all get your turn.

111
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:55,950
Sir.

112
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,110
Sir.

113
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,880
Bury her in the Pen Grave.

114
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:11,070
No...

115
00:06:12,230 --> 00:06:13,040
No...

116
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,920
Somebody help!

117
00:06:25,670 --> 00:06:28,840
Want to try something new?

118
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:34,100
You idiot!

119
00:06:36,410 --> 00:06:37,440
You wretched scum!

120
00:06:37,550 --> 00:06:38,830
You dared offend my esteemed guest?

121
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,270
I'll kill you!

122
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:42,040
Sir!

123
00:06:42,390 --> 00:06:43,490
Spare me, please!

124
00:06:46,230 --> 00:06:46,880
Sir.

125
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,350
Sir,

126
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,670
Madam has returned to the estate.

127
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:52,940
Why didn't you say so earlier?

128
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,200
Drinking ends here for today.

129
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,110
Everyone, disperse!

130
00:06:58,270 --> 00:06:59,070
Mr. Luan,

131
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:00,230
why are you leaving?

132
00:07:00,230 --> 00:07:01,640
My wife has returned!

133
00:07:03,070 --> 00:07:03,920
Ma,

134
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,440
his lioness is back!

135
00:07:08,790 --> 00:07:09,550
Gu,

136
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,670
I can now confirm for sure

137
00:07:11,670 --> 00:07:13,480
that Zhao Ban is in Yayuan Mansion.

138
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,350
Take your men to find her immediately!

139
00:07:15,350 --> 00:07:16,830
If you're late, it'll be too late!

140
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,340
Wan Fu, gather the team!

141
00:07:19,490 --> 00:07:20,730
Surround Yayuan Mansion with all haste!

142
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:49,950
Are you still trying to run?

143
00:07:52,670 --> 00:07:53,830
[Wu Mei]
There's no way out.

144
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:57,720
If you still have the energy

145
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:59,070
to say such pointless things,

146
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:01,420
why not think of a plan with me instead?

147
00:08:05,110 --> 00:08:07,480
Those animals beat people to death in broad daylight!

148
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,720
You saw it with your own eyes.

149
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,270
How can you just stay here and do nothing?

150
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,270
You're such a strange girl.

151
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,140
Someone else died.

152
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:17,320
Why are you so anxious?

153
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:19,440
That dead person was my neighbor's sister-in-law.

154
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:21,110
How could I not be worried?

155
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:23,070
I don't want to die.

156
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,600
My family is still waiting for me.

157
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,830
Is that so?

158
00:08:29,070 --> 00:08:30,320
I envy you.

159
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:42,880
Earlier,

160
00:08:43,590 --> 00:08:45,000
why did you help me?

161
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,100
It was nothing.

162
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:48,180
I just did it.

163
00:08:50,670 --> 00:08:51,790
My name is Zhao Ban.

164
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:53,440
What's yours?

165
00:08:54,790 --> 00:08:55,800
We're dying people.

166
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,110
No need to exchange names.

167
00:08:58,110 --> 00:08:58,840
There is a need.

168
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:01,960
If I escape,

169
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:04,150
I'll go to your family and let them know.

170
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,440
I have no family.

171
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,710
No one in this world cares for me.

172
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:14,200
I...

173
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:15,670
I'll care for you.

174
00:09:30,590 --> 00:09:31,760
I know a few ways out.

175
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,060
If you can make it out,

176
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,840
consider it your fortune.

177
00:09:49,860 --> 00:09:53,660
[Zou Ziyin, Daughter of Zou Mian]

178
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,640
Alright,

179
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:11,020
you may leave now.

180
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:26,230
I'll attend to you myself.

181
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,150
Come on.

182
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:37,620
Come on, dear.

183
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:39,880
Try the water. Is it warm enough?

184
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:43,030
It's fine.

185
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:47,000
Dear,

186
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:49,030
to think a few old books

187
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,790
brought in so much gold,

188
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:53,910
we owe it to the banned books of our dynasty.

189
00:10:55,230 --> 00:10:56,110
Hey...

190
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:57,880
It's all thanks to my father!

191
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,550
Those connections of yours

192
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:02,280
were all introduced by my father!

193
00:11:03,150 --> 00:11:04,200
Yes.

194
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:05,790
Other than the Zou family,

195
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,710
who else would dare run such a business?

196
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:10,230
Dear,

197
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:13,150
you should keep your feet warm.

198
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,000
Your Taixi acupoint

199
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,590
is cold and weak.

200
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,590
Didn't the doctor warn you?

201
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:22,550
It could lead to period pain.

202
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,590
Isn't it because of your incompetence?

203
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,030
Alright,

204
00:11:29,030 --> 00:11:30,840
it's all my fault.

205
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:34,200
You need to be grateful.

206
00:11:34,350 --> 00:11:35,200
Grateful!

207
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,440
Of course, I'm grateful.

208
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,550
Tonight,

209
00:11:38,550 --> 00:11:40,760
I'll properly serve you, dear.

210
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,320
Don't think I'm not aware

211
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,080
of the tricks you use in Yayuan Mansion.

212
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:49,230
Officials just love that kind of thing.

213
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,640
I'm only accompanying them.

214
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,550
And I'm doing it all for Father, too.

215
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,150
Ban.

216
00:12:50,350 --> 00:12:51,640
Don't be scared. It's me.

217
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:52,790
Ci!

218
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,110
How did you get here?

219
00:12:57,110 --> 00:12:58,150
Su

220
00:12:58,150 --> 00:12:59,320
asked me to come find you.

221
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,470
It's all my fault you're in this mess.

222
00:13:03,150 --> 00:13:04,030
Thank you.

223
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,230
Don't say that.

224
00:13:05,590 --> 00:13:07,320
Didn't you just save me earlier?

225
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:09,110
You deliberately smashed that wine bottle, didn't you?

226
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,110
This isn't the place to talk.

227
00:13:13,110 --> 00:13:13,670
Come with me.

228
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:14,200
Alright.

229
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:20,150
What is this?

230
00:13:20,350 --> 00:13:21,280
The sketches

231
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:24,030
of the two murder suspects involved in the Fan Building case.

232
00:13:24,350 --> 00:13:25,550
I brought them just for you.

233
00:13:25,790 --> 00:13:28,030
Don't die in confusion at someone else's hands!

234
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,280
Give it to me.

235
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:34,880
Dear.

236
00:13:41,230 --> 00:13:43,150
You really care about me!

237
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,080
Here.

238
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:46,080
Take care.

239
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:56,260
[Notice from Kaifeng Court: Runaways Ci and Lu Sanzhen Wanted]

240
00:14:01,790 --> 00:14:02,910
Where are you going?

241
00:14:03,520 --> 00:14:04,910
That despicable murderer

242
00:14:04,910 --> 00:14:06,230
has already sneaked into Yayuan Mansion!

243
00:14:06,230 --> 00:14:08,030
I'm going to skin her alive!

244
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,030
It's alright.

245
00:14:23,030 --> 00:14:23,790
Don't be afraid.

246
00:14:28,710 --> 00:14:29,880
This is Yayuan Mansion's account ledger.

247
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,160
[Yayuan Mansion Expense Ledger]

248
00:14:31,190 --> 00:14:32,760
It contains evidence of the Zou family bribing officials.

249
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:41,960
Hold on to it for me.

250
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:44,840
Here's a map to get out of here.

251
00:14:56,490 --> 00:14:57,610
Your dagger for self-defense.

252
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:03,410
You didn't mess around with any of this, did you?

253
00:15:04,230 --> 00:15:05,760
My wife and child are in your hands.

254
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:06,550
How would I dare?

255
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:07,760
Rest assured,

256
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,960
they're already safe at home.

257
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:11,670
That's great...

258
00:15:14,910 --> 00:15:16,320
But you've done too much evil.

259
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:19,110
I can't let you go.

260
00:15:23,790 --> 00:15:24,790
Let's go.

261
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:26,760
You... you killed him.

262
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:29,230
They killed Yingying

263
00:15:29,230 --> 00:15:30,440
and so many others!

264
00:15:31,350 --> 00:15:33,400
The names on that red silk from the Fan Building

265
00:15:33,710 --> 00:15:36,200
are all innocent women they murdered.

266
00:15:36,590 --> 00:15:38,080
I risked my life to sneak in here

267
00:15:38,350 --> 00:15:40,400
just to get evidence of their crimes.

268
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:43,200
With this ledger,

269
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,790
we can uproot them completely.

270
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:48,470
No one wants to bring them to justice more than I do.

271
00:15:48,590 --> 00:15:49,960
If you want revenge too,

272
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,350
then come with me.

273
00:15:58,900 --> 00:16:04,020
[Yayuan Mansion]

274
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:06,320
Tie Chi, Fei Jian!

275
00:16:06,470 --> 00:16:07,000
Here!

276
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:07,840
Take action!

277
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:22,670
Ban!

278
00:16:23,230 --> 00:16:23,760
Ban!

279
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:24,840
Zhao Ban!

280
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:25,960
Ban, where are you?

281
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:26,640
Wan Fu!

282
00:16:26,710 --> 00:16:27,520
The back mountain!

283
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:29,550
You, come with me to the back mountain!

284
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:30,140
Yes, sir!

285
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:36,520
This woman's death

286
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:38,000
isn't much of a concern,

287
00:16:38,150 --> 00:16:39,230
but now we have to dig a pit for her.

288
00:16:39,230 --> 00:16:40,080
Yeah.

289
00:16:40,470 --> 00:16:41,670
If it were like before,

290
00:16:41,910 --> 00:16:43,030
