00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:58,960
What else can we do at this point?

584
00:29:00,350 --> 00:29:01,750
I'll go find it myself!

585
00:29:17,230 --> 00:29:18,080
Mr. He...

586
00:29:19,870 --> 00:29:20,840
I'm sorry to have involved you.

587
00:29:21,840 --> 00:29:22,560
It's nothing.

588
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:26,960
Thank you for helping me

589
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,150
keep the ledger a secret.

590
00:29:29,990 --> 00:29:32,080
But why did you help me?

591
00:29:34,840 --> 00:29:36,510
I didn't set out to help you.

592
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:38,580
I just didn't know how to react

593
00:29:38,770 --> 00:29:39,690
at the time,

594
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:41,630
and I ended up locked up here with you

595
00:29:41,630 --> 00:29:42,640
before I knew it.

596
00:29:44,110 --> 00:29:44,990
Still,

597
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:47,600
Headmistress Chi did act rather oddly today.

598
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:52,200
Who would've thought she's the headmistress,

599
00:29:52,350 --> 00:29:54,440
a cold-hearted courtesan with no principles.

600
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:54,990
You're not right!

601
00:29:56,320 --> 00:29:57,960
She may have a temper,

602
00:29:57,960 --> 00:29:59,560
but she's definitely a good person.

603
00:30:00,080 --> 00:30:01,350
She herself was an orphan.

604
00:30:01,630 --> 00:30:02,990
She can't bear to see these children

605
00:30:02,990 --> 00:30:04,530
endure the same suffering she did.

606
00:30:05,150 --> 00:30:06,840
To keep the welfare center running,

607
00:30:07,720 --> 00:30:08,750
she travels everywhere performing.

608
00:30:09,350 --> 00:30:11,350
She doesn't spend a single coin of the money she earns.

609
00:30:11,350 --> 00:30:12,510
She's a good person.

610
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:15,510
Alright.

611
00:30:18,150 --> 00:30:19,920
But given her ways,

612
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:21,630
I'm not comfortable entrusting her with the ledger.

613
00:30:22,110 --> 00:30:22,870
The ledger...

614
00:30:23,200 --> 00:30:23,560
Oh no,

615
00:30:23,560 --> 00:30:25,170
I need to find a way out of here.

616
00:30:28,030 --> 00:30:29,350
If she gets her hands on that ledger,

617
00:30:29,350 --> 00:30:30,390
that would be bad.

618
00:30:35,600 --> 00:30:36,600
Mr. He,

619
00:30:37,390 --> 00:30:39,480
could you think of a way to help me?

620
00:30:39,840 --> 00:30:41,080
You're locked up here.

621
00:30:41,200 --> 00:30:42,440
Won't your family worry

622
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:43,560
if they can't find you?

623
00:30:46,750 --> 00:30:47,600
I don't have any family.

624
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:58,800
Oh, I'm sorry, Mr. He.

625
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:00,920
I didn't know about that.

626
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:02,270
I apologize.

627
00:31:02,680 --> 00:31:04,230
It's fine.

628
00:31:04,990 --> 00:31:06,480
There's no need to apologize.

629
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:17,760
Then...

630
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,440
have you ever tried looking for your family?

631
00:31:23,630 --> 00:31:24,630
I couldn't find them.

632
00:31:25,840 --> 00:31:26,750
You couldn't find them?

633
00:31:27,440 --> 00:31:28,600
They died...

634
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:31,030
right in front of me.

635
00:31:37,350 --> 00:31:38,230
It's alright.

636
00:31:38,560 --> 00:31:39,740
It happened a long time ago.

637
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:52,320
Here we are!

638
00:31:52,990 --> 00:31:53,390
Quick!

639
00:31:55,390 --> 00:31:55,960
Here!

640
00:31:57,390 --> 00:31:57,990
Ban!

641
00:31:58,920 --> 00:31:59,510
Ban!

642
00:32:01,080 --> 00:32:01,750
Ban!

643
00:32:03,350 --> 00:32:04,680
Zhao Ban!

644
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,110
Zhao Ban!

645
00:32:06,750 --> 00:32:07,270
This way!

646
00:32:09,110 --> 00:32:09,800
Ban!

647
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:14,110
Ban!

648
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:16,320
Ban!

649
00:32:16,870 --> 00:32:17,440
Ban!

650
00:32:19,150 --> 00:32:21,080
I knew you'd come here soon.

651
00:32:22,080 --> 00:32:22,840
Mrs.,

652
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:24,840
my sister is named Zhao Ban.

653
00:32:24,840 --> 00:32:25,960
I heard she's here with you.

654
00:32:26,080 --> 00:32:27,080
Do you know her?

655
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:29,920
Your sister is safe now.

656
00:32:30,080 --> 00:32:30,990
Rest assured.

657
00:32:31,840 --> 00:32:32,720
Thank you!

658
00:32:32,750 --> 00:32:33,720
You know us?

659
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:34,320
Of course.

660
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:37,320
You truly carry yourself with distinction.

661
00:32:38,350 --> 00:32:40,600
I've always wanted to test your skills.

662
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:42,390
How do you know about me?

663
00:32:42,560 --> 00:32:43,560
Enough talk!

664
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:44,750
Zhao Buyou,

665
00:32:44,750 --> 00:32:45,510
Yao He,

666
00:32:45,720 --> 00:32:46,920
go find Ban.

667
00:32:48,080 --> 00:32:49,680
Got it. Be careful.

668
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:53,390
Zhao Ban!

669
00:32:53,390 --> 00:32:53,920
Ban!

670
00:32:55,390 --> 00:32:56,150
Ban!

671
00:32:56,350 --> 00:32:57,080
Zhao Ban!

672
00:32:59,510 --> 00:33:00,270
Zhao Ban!

673
00:33:00,270 --> 00:33:00,960
Ban!

674
00:33:01,510 --> 00:33:02,270
You search that side!

675
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:02,840
Alright!

676
00:33:06,990 --> 00:33:07,960
Today,

677
00:33:08,030 --> 00:33:09,350
I'm going to challenge you!

678
00:33:32,680 --> 00:33:33,390
Zhao Ban!

679
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:34,350
Ban!

680
00:33:34,600 --> 00:33:35,350
Let's split up and search!

681
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:35,840
Alright.

682
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:37,230
Ban!

683
00:33:43,630 --> 00:33:44,200
Ban!

684
00:33:45,350 --> 00:33:46,150
Ban!

685
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:48,350
Ban!

686
00:34:03,230 --> 00:34:04,990
With your clumsy skills,

687
00:34:05,480 --> 00:34:07,150
you think you can take me on?

688
00:34:08,200 --> 00:34:08,870
Speak,

689
00:34:09,550 --> 00:34:10,350
who are you,

690
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:11,680
and why are you targeting me?

691
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:14,200
I'm someone who lives in your shadow,

692
00:34:14,550 --> 00:34:15,830
unable to see the light,

693
00:34:16,390 --> 00:34:17,870
destined for a miserable end.

694
00:34:18,790 --> 00:34:20,390
Living in my shadow?

695
00:34:20,720 --> 00:34:21,680
What do you mean?

696
00:34:22,240 --> 00:34:23,870
- Why would you... - Search inside!

697
00:34:28,200 --> 00:34:29,070
She came looking for you?

698
00:34:29,790 --> 00:34:30,680
Why is she here?

699
00:34:30,720 --> 00:34:31,390
Who is she?

700
00:34:31,390 --> 00:34:33,110
Zou Mian's daughter, Zou Ziyin.

701
00:34:39,110 --> 00:34:41,310
Sneaking around and targeting the Zou family,

702
00:34:41,790 --> 00:34:44,310
did you think I wouldn't find this shabby place?

703
00:34:46,630 --> 00:34:48,790
Hand over the ledger from Yayuan Mansion.

704
00:34:50,110 --> 00:34:51,000
Otherwise,

705
00:34:51,310 --> 00:34:52,150
you'll end up

706
00:34:52,390 --> 00:34:53,480
just like her!

707
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:56,790
Sanzhen!

708
00:34:58,630 --> 00:35:00,240
I was the one who placed the orders these past few days

709
00:35:00,790 --> 00:35:02,070
for you to go against the Zou family.

710
00:35:02,720 --> 00:35:04,310
Now they've come to our doorstep.

711
00:35:04,550 --> 00:35:05,630
You took my money.

712
00:35:06,040 --> 00:35:07,070
You should resolve my troubles.

713
00:35:10,550 --> 00:35:12,760
So many people risked their lives to retrieve it.

714
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:14,240
How could I possibly give it back to you?

715
00:35:14,920 --> 00:35:16,000
You won't hand it over?

716
00:35:17,040 --> 00:35:17,830
Fine.

717
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:20,200
Flatten this place!

718
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:21,240
Yes!

719
00:35:22,680 --> 00:35:24,110
If you help me today,

720
00:35:24,600 --> 00:35:26,680
we'll be even, and I won't trouble you again.

721
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:29,170
As for the orders, we'll discuss later.

722
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:34,480
Hurry up!

723
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:00,680
There's one more!

724
00:36:57,150 --> 00:36:57,830
Ban!

725
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:05,040
What are you doing here?

726
00:37:05,310 --> 00:37:07,480
We heard a noise outside,

727
00:37:07,480 --> 00:37:09,680
got scared, and hid here.

728
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:10,240
Alright,

729
00:37:10,630 --> 00:37:11,960
just stay here.

730
00:37:11,960 --> 00:37:13,150
Don't make any noise!

731
00:37:14,040 --> 00:37:15,580
Stay hidden and keep quiet!

732
00:37:15,580 --> 00:37:16,390
Everyone, stay quiet!

733
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:24,440
Ban!

734
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:30,150
Remember this:

735
00:37:30,350 --> 00:37:31,720
the secret to martial arts lies

736
00:37:32,040 --> 00:37:34,000
in focusing all your energy

737
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,150
into your hands.

738
00:37:35,790 --> 00:37:37,240
Imagine they're made of iron,

739
00:37:38,070 --> 00:37:38,830
unbreakable.

740
00:37:58,040 --> 00:37:59,240
Kaifeng Court is investigating!

741
00:37:59,280 --> 00:38:00,440
Arrest everyone!

742
00:38:10,790 --> 00:38:11,830
Arrest them all!

743
00:38:12,070 --> 00:38:12,680
Yes!

744
00:38:15,870 --> 00:38:16,680
Squat down, don't move!

745
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:17,630
Don't leave!

746
00:38:17,630 --> 00:38:19,040
- Squat down! - Let's see who dares to touch me!

747
00:38:19,790 --> 00:38:21,070
Mere Kaifeng Court,

748
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:22,440
do you know who my father is?

749
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,280
Take her!

750
00:38:26,350 --> 00:38:26,920
You...

751
00:38:27,070 --> 00:38:28,280
you must have a death wish!

752
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:37,830
Where's Ban?

753
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:39,110
Ban!

754
00:38:39,520 --> 00:38:40,550
- Yao He! - Ban, where are you?

755
00:38:40,550 --> 00:38:41,630
Yao He, I'm over here!

756
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:42,330
- Ban! - Yao He!

757
00:38:42,330 --> 00:38:43,440
Move aside. I'm breaking in!

758
00:38:43,720 --> 00:38:44,440
What?

759
00:38:44,630 --> 00:38:45,200
You...

760
00:38:48,350 --> 00:38:49,150
Hold on!

761
00:38:49,240 --> 00:38:51,070
I'll take you to treat your injuries now.

762
00:38:51,070 --> 00:38:52,550
What are you doing?

763
00:38:52,830 --> 00:38:53,940
I'm taking you to get treated!

764
00:38:53,940 --> 00:38:55,150
I... I'm fine.

765
00:38:55,150 --> 00:38:56,570
Mr. He is still watching.

766
00:38:56,570 --> 00:38:57,970
Put me down now!

767
00:39:02,830 --> 00:39:03,720
Where are you going?

768
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:05,150
I need to find that ledger!

769
00:39:05,150 --> 00:39:06,200
Hey, wait for me!

770
00:39:06,200 --> 00:39:06,720
It's dangerous!

771
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:07,960
Oh, hey...

772
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:14,720
Stop struggling!

773
00:39:15,390 --> 00:39:15,870
Move!

774
00:39:15,870 --> 00:39:16,480
Let go of me!

775
00:39:16,830 --> 00:39:17,350
Move!

776
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:20,150
Check every room thoroughly!

777
00:39:20,550 --> 00:39:21,550
Don't leave anyone behind!

778
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:27,760
Dear,

779
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,480
I'm afraid this lady won't make it.

780
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:32,070
I don't know what her connection to the Fan Building case is.

781
00:39:32,830 --> 00:39:35,040
She told me she's the one who placed the orders,

782
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:37,790
but I doubt it.

783
00:39:37,790 --> 00:39:38,870
She also said

784
00:39:38,870 --> 00:39:40,760
she lives in my shadow.

785
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:41,480
Where are they?

786
00:39:41,550 --> 00:39:42,200
Buyou!

787
00:39:43,150 --> 00:39:44,110
Buyou! Wen Yue!

788
00:39:45,110 --> 00:39:45,760
- Ban! - Buyou!

789
00:39:45,760 --> 00:39:46,350
- Are you alright? - Wen Yue!

790
00:39:46,350 --> 00:39:47,040
You're not hurt, are you?

791
00:39:47,040 --> 00:39:47,680
I'm fine!

792
00:39:47,790 --> 00:39:49,000
I need to meet Inspector Gu!

793
00:39:49,110 --> 00:39:49,870
I need to meet Inspector Gu...

794
00:39:49,870 --> 00:39:50,590
Ban,

795
00:39:51,070 --> 00:39:51,720
are you alright?

796
00:39:51,720 --> 00:39:52,520
I'm fine.

797
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:53,150
Inspector Gu,

798
00:39:53,200 --> 00:39:54,310
this is the ledger the embroiderers and I

799
00:39:54,310 --> 00:39:56,150
risked our lives to retrieve from Yayuan Mansion.

800
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:58,680
They said it contains evidence to bring down the Zou family.

