806
00:40:33,100 --> 00:40:38,420
♪I see misty rain over countless homes♪

807
00:40:38,740 --> 00:40:42,620
♪Countless homes♪

808
00:40:43,720 --> 00:40:44,440
Well...

809
00:40:44,830 --> 00:40:45,590
You're fine?

810
00:40:45,830 --> 00:40:46,440
You...

811
00:40:46,790 --> 00:40:47,440
Are you really fine?

812
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:48,760
I'm fine, really.

813
00:40:49,680 --> 00:40:50,280
Zhao Ban!

814
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:51,760
You've become so daring,

815
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:52,680
venturing out alone into danger.

816
00:40:52,680 --> 00:40:53,630
What if something happened?

817
00:40:53,630 --> 00:40:55,440
I was already very cautious, okay?

818
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:56,790
Those people are too devious!

819
00:40:56,790 --> 00:40:58,040
That's just an excuse!

820
00:40:58,040 --> 00:40:59,390
Why are you so harsh?

821
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:01,310
Can't you show some concern for me?

822
00:41:02,070 --> 00:41:02,790
What's going on?

823
00:41:03,550 --> 00:41:04,550
Buyou, Wen Yue...

824
00:41:04,550 --> 00:41:05,760
The moment he got back,

825
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:06,590
he started scolding me,

826
00:41:06,590 --> 00:41:07,480
- criticizing me, pointing fingers... - Buyou!

827
00:41:07,480 --> 00:41:08,400
Stop always defending her!

828
00:41:08,400 --> 00:41:09,870
What if something really happens to her?

829
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:10,960
Wen Yue,

830
00:41:11,150 --> 00:41:13,040
why didn't you tell me about something this big?

831
00:41:13,040 --> 00:41:14,830
I had to hear it from the Office of Justice!

832
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:19,000
Buyou was worried you'd get anxious like this

833
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:20,040
and insisted on following us.

834
00:41:20,110 --> 00:41:21,390
Then wouldn't you be in danger too?

835
00:41:22,040 --> 00:41:23,200
Your sister just got frightened.

836
00:41:23,200 --> 00:41:24,720
Can't you comfort her a little?

837
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,680
Exactly! He never comforts me!

838
00:41:28,790 --> 00:41:29,350
Enough about it.

839
00:41:29,680 --> 00:41:30,920
I know all about the crimes

840
00:41:31,070 --> 00:41:32,960
Luan Hui committed at Yayuan Mansion.

841
00:41:33,070 --> 00:41:34,680
He's worse than an animal!

842
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:36,480
Speaking of Luan Hui,

843
00:41:36,920 --> 00:41:38,720
now the authorities can't find him anywhere.

844
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:39,790
Where could he be?

845
00:41:40,590 --> 00:41:41,350
Exactly.

846
00:41:43,440 --> 00:41:45,040
Dear, what are you thinking?

847
00:41:47,830 --> 00:41:48,720
I'm thinking...

848
00:41:49,350 --> 00:41:51,040
if I were him, what would I do?

849
00:41:52,520 --> 00:41:53,890
Kaifeng Court has already investigated

850
00:41:53,890 --> 00:41:55,760
most of the people present that night.

851
00:41:56,010 --> 00:41:56,520
Ban,

852
00:41:57,110 --> 00:41:58,070
you said

853
00:41:58,070 --> 00:42:00,720
that night at Yayuan Mansion, aside from those two corrupt officials,

854
00:42:01,110 --> 00:42:03,150
there was a foreigner with the surname Cui?

855
00:42:04,240 --> 00:42:06,000
Yes, that's right.

856
00:42:06,870 --> 00:42:07,960
Although he looked

857
00:42:07,960 --> 00:42:09,480
no different from us,

858
00:42:09,520 --> 00:42:11,590
it was clear he was a foreigner by the way he spoke.

859
00:42:11,680 --> 00:42:13,070
He had a lisp.

860
00:42:13,560 --> 00:42:14,370
Yes,

861
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:16,110
when those foreigners speak,

862
00:42:16,110 --> 00:42:18,240
it sounds like they have a lisp.

863
00:42:19,150 --> 00:42:21,440
What nonsense is this?

864
00:42:22,440 --> 00:42:23,150
Father,

865
00:42:23,830 --> 00:42:25,240
how do you even know such things?

866
00:42:27,390 --> 00:42:29,110
Your grandfather and I...

867
00:42:29,110 --> 00:42:30,280
No,

868
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:31,760
when your grandfather and I were young,

869
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:33,520
we often saw foreigners

870
00:42:33,590 --> 00:42:36,040
at the palace, bringing gifts.

